-----------
README

Run offline MC6 ice optical scheme

Yi-Hsuan Chen
yihsuan@umich.edu
-----------

Step:

1. Edit zz-mc6.f90 to change parameter values
	iciwp: in-cloud ice water path (kg/m2)
	deis : ice effectice diameter (microns)
	band : print optical depth at this band on screen

2. type 'make' to complie the all the codes. The execute file is 'test111'

3. type './test111'. The optical depth at the given band will be printed on screen.

** If needed, type 'make clean' to remove all objects

